text: Det drønner gjennom dalen () is a 1938 Norwegian drama film written and directed by Olav Dalgard, starring Tryggve Larssen and Ragnhild Hald. It follows the trials and tribulations of contemporary lumberjacks. ==External links== * * * Det drønner gjennom dalen at the Norwegian Film Institute Category:1938 films Category:1938 drama films Category:Norwegian films Category:Norwegian black-and-white films Category:Norwegian drama films
